Package com.dimon.protocol

Class MyUDPProtocol

java.lang.Object
com.dimon.protocol.MyUDPProtocol
public class MyUDPProtocol extends Object
Represents a custom UDP protocol for transmitting data. This class defines the structure of the protocol, including fields for sequence numbers, type of message, checksum, window size, flags, and data. It also provides methods for serialization and deserialization of the protocol into byte arrays.

This class supports handling both message and file data, including converting protocol objects to byte arrays and parsing byte arrays into protocol objects.

Features include: - Handling sequence numbers and type of messages. - Generating byte arrays with optional data or file content. - Support for checksum validation and flags.
